<ext_description linkend="Product_occurrence_mim.restrict_part_occurrence">
The <b>restrict_part_occurrence</b> rule constrains every instance of <b>product_definition</b> of type 'part_occurrence'.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Product_occurrence_mim.restrict_part_occurrence.wr:wr1">
Every instance of <b>product_definition</b> of type 'part_occurrence' shall be a definition of a product of type either <b>single_instance</b>, 
<b>selected instance</b>, <b>quantified instance</b> or <b>specified instance</b>. 
</ext_description>
